# Pawtoberfest Update – pets invasion begins!

The Wiesn just got a whole lot cuter – pets are here! Meet Briny, Teddy, and Pomkin: three lovable companions ready to bond, grow, and explore Oktoberfest with you. 

[media]

[media]

[media]

**What’s New in Pawtoberfest?**

🐱 New Pets – Unique personalities, adorable animations & color rarities (common to epic).

 📊 Care System – Manage happiness, hunger, stamina & XP to help your pet thrive.

 🎮 Pet Trial – Try a pet for free! Keep it by leveling to 5 or buy it at a reduced price.

 🛍️ Pet Shop – Adopt more pets with Pet Shards and expand your fluffy collection.

 👕 Pet-Inspired Outfits – Match your look to your new best friend in cozy, themed styles!

**Plus all your Oktoberfest favorites:**

🎯 Classic Fairground Games

 🎢 Thrilling Rides

 👗 Avatar Customization

 🎤 Social Fun & Mini-Games

Whether you’re bonding with Briny or dressing like Teddy, Pawtoberfest is your cutest Wiesn yet! 🧡🐾
